title: Porcelain and the Tramps DEMO songs
description: Porcelain and the Tramps are an industrial rock band from Detroit, Michigan, but working from LA, California. Singer/songwriter, Alaina Beaton is the only official member of the band, though she is currently in the studio with John Lowery (more commonly known as John 5 - the current guitarist for industrial band Rob Zombie, and former guitarist for rock group Marilyn Manson), producers Lester Mendez and Bobby Huff, among others
